{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/eudiwalletkit\/getstarted"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Package-installation","level":2,"text":"Package installation","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To use EUDI Wallet Kit, add the following dependency to your Package.swift:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["dependencies: [","\t\t.package(url: \"https:\/\/github.com\/eu-digital-identity-wallet\/eudi-lib-ios-wallet-kit.git\", .upToNextMajor(from: \"0.6.6\"))","]"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then add the Eudi Wallet package to your target’s dependencies:"}]},{"code":["dependencies: [","\t\t.product(name: \"EudiWalletKit\", package: \"eudi-lib-ios-wallet-kit\"),","]"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Initialization","anchor":"Initialization"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/EudiWallet"},{"type":"text","text":" class provides a unified API for the two user attestation presentation flows. It is initialized with a document storage manager instance. For SwiftUI apps, the wallet instance can be added as an "},{"code":"environmentObject","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to be accessible from all views. A KeyChain implementation of document storage is available."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\tlet certificates = [\"pidissuerca02_cz\", \"pidissuerca02_ee\", \"pidissuerca02_eu\", \"pidissuerca02_lu\", \"pidissuerca02_nl\", \"pidissuerca02_pt\", \"pidissuerca02_ut\"]","    wallet = try! EudiWallet(serviceName: \"my_wallet_app\", trustedReaderCertificates: certificates.map { Data(name: $0, ext: \"der\")! }, logFileName: \"temp.txt\")","    wallet.userAuthenticationRequired = true","    wallet.openID4VpConfig = OpenId4VpConfiguration(clientIdSchemes: [.x509SanDns, .x509Hash])","    wallet.transactionLogger = MyFileTransactionLogger(wallet: wallet)","\twallet.loadAllDocuments()"]},{"text":"OpenID4VCI Configuration","anchor":"OpenID4VCI-Configuration","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The wallet now supports multiple OpenID4VCI issuer configurations for enhanced flexibility. You can configure the wallet with a dictionary of issuer configurations:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Configure multiple OpenID4VCI issuers with DPoP support","let issuerConfigurations: [String: OpenId4VciConfiguration] = [","    \"eudi_pid_issuer\": OpenId4VciConfiguration(","        credentialIssuerURL: \"https:\/\/pid.issuer.example.com\",","        useDpopIfSupported: true,","        dpopKeyOptions: KeyOptions(","            secureAreaName: \"SecureEnclave\", curve: .P256, accessControl: .requireUserPresence","        )","    ),","    \"mdl_issuer\": OpenId4VciConfiguration(","        credentialIssuerURL: \"https:\/\/mdl.issuer.example.com\",","        useDpopIfSupported: false","    )","]","","\/\/ Register additional issuers after initialization","try wallet.registerOpenId4VciServices(issuerConfigurations)"],"syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/ManageDocuments","doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/SecureAreas","doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/PresentationService","doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/WalletUI"],"anchor":"Essentials","title":"Essentials"}],"metadata":{"role":"article","title":"Get started","roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"EudiWalletKit"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"How to install and initialize EUDI Wallet Kit in your project"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/GetStart